import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'
import {
  CCard,
  CCardBody,
  CCardGroup,
  CCardHeader,
  CAlert
} from '@coreui/react'
import {
  CChartBar,
  CChartLine,
  CChartDoughnut,
  CChartRadar,
  CChartPie,
  CChartPolarArea
} from '@coreui/react-chartjs'
import { DocsLink } from 'src/reusable'

const AvailabilityAndLosses = () => {

  return (
    <CCard>
      <CCardHeader>
        Weather Forecast
      </CCardHeader>
      <CCardBody>
        
              <CAlert color="primary">Coming Soon</CAlert>
      </CCardBody>
    </CCard>
  )
}

export default AvailabilityAndLosses
